list_page_teaser: Sarah & Jacob have been going together for many years.  Click to learn more!
description_html:
Sarah and Jacob are the parents of a still-relatively-young daughter, and have been together for many years.

Hopefully they will share some of their tips for how they make their relationship last. Check back soon for updates!
story_html:
I met Sarah and Jacob at the Goth clubs in Denver and Fort Collins here in Colorado.

They have relocated to the Pacific Northwest and we have been out of touch. I wanted to have something for them to look at before asking them to share their story.

I will share more information as it becomes available. To learn when I update the site, follow us on social media or join the email list!

image_list.title: Sarah
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: The Red and Yellow in Sarah's spiritual portrait say she is passionate and down-to-earth.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Red in this portrait represents Sarah's dominant trait, her passion.  In Extraverts, the dominant trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long vertical line to represent this, because it is the side of their personality that is most evident.
image_list.explain_aux: The Yellow in this portrait represents Sarah's auxiliary trait, her pragmatism.  In Extraverts, the auxiliary trait is directed inwardly and is less evident than the dominant trait.
image_list.story_html:
Sarah lives in Corvallis, Oregon.

I will share more information as it becomes available.
